with-picasa is photo uploader to picasa.
----------------------------------------
Post photos taken by motion(*), and delete photos from Picasa.
"watchcat" is the name that is I monitor for my pet cat.

 * http://motion.sf.net
 
1. Install Debian package googlecl.
   $ sudo apt-get install googlecl

2. register crontab entry.
   $ crontab -e
   --
   3-59/15 * * * * ~/postphoto.sh
   8-59/15 * * * * ~/deletephoto.sh

 -- Kouhei Maeda <mkouhei at palmtb.net>, Sat, 9 Jul 2011 01:56:15 +0900
